# Image Directory

This directory contains images for the portfolio website.

## Required Images:

1. **portrait.jpg** (384x384 or larger)
   - Professional headshot of Ashish Singh
   - Should be high quality and well-lit
   - Used in the Hero section

2. **ashish-singh-og.webp** (1200x630)
   - Open Graph image for social media sharing
   - Should include name and title text overlay
   - Optimized WebP format for fast loading

## Image Guidelines:

- Use WebP format when possible for better compression
- Ensure images are optimized for web (compressed but high quality)
- Include proper alt text for accessibility
- Use responsive images with appropriate sizes

## SEO Benefits:

- Images help with Google Image Search visibility
- Proper alt text improves accessibility and SEO
- Open Graph images improve social media sharing
- Image sitemap helps search engines index visual content